  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe the combined effect of interference and diffraction with two slits, each with finite width</item>
<item>Determine the relative intensities of interference fringes within a diffraction pattern</item>
<item>Identify missing orders, if any</item></list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
